### 6. Security and Trust
For security and peace of mind, it is strongly recommended to use extensions from developers who clearly identify themselves with real-world contact information.  
Anonymous creators are not necessarily malicious, but if harm occurs, accountability may be impossible to enforce.  
Server owners should carefully evaluate this risk when choosing extensions.

